quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  26,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  26,1,Taa-Seeen-Meeem
  26,2,Tilka Aayaatul Kitaabil Mubeen
  26,3,La'allaka baakhi'un nafsaka allaa yakoonoo mu'mineen
  26,4,In nashaa nunazzil 'alaihim minas samaaa'i Aayatan fazallat a'naaquhum lahaa khaadi'een
  26,5,Wa maa yaateehim min zikrim minar Rahmaani muhdasin illaa kaanoo 'anhu mu'rideen
  26,6,Faqad kazzaboo fasa yaateehim ambaaa'u maa kaanoo bihee yastahzi'oon
  26,7,Awa lam yaraw ilal ardi kam ambatnaa feehaa min kulli zawjin kareem
  26,8,Inn fee zaalika la Aayah; wa maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen
  26,9,Wa inna Rabbaka la Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 1)
  26,10,Wa iz naadaa Rabbuka Moosaaa ani'-til qawmaz zaalimeen
  26,11,Qawma Fir'awn; alaa yattaqoon
  26,12,Qaala Rabbi inneee akhaafu ai yukazziboon
  26,13,Wa yadeequ sadree wa laa yantaliqu lisaanee fa arsil ilaa Haaroon
  26,14,Wa lahum 'alaiya zambun fa akhaafu ai yaqtuloon
  26,15,Qaala kallaa fazhabaa bi Aayaatinaaa innaa ma'akum mustami'oon
  26,16,Faatiyaa Fir'awna faqoolaaa innaa Rasoolu Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,17,An arsil ma'anaa Baneee Israaa'eel
  26,18,Qaala alam nurabbika feenaa waleedanw wa labista feenaa min 'umurika sineen
  26,19,Wa fa'alta fa'latakal latee fa'alta wa anta minal kaafireen
  26,20,Qaala fa'altuhaaa izanw wa ana minad daaaleen
  26,21,Fafarartu minkum lam maa khiftukum fawahaba lee Rabbee hukmanw wa ja'alanee minal mursaleen
  26,22,Wa tilka ni'matun tamun nuhaa 'alaiya an 'abbatta Baneee Israaa'eel
  26,23,Qaala Fir'awnu wa maa Rabbul 'aalameen
  26,24,Qaala Rabbus samaawaati wal ardi wa maa bainahumaa in kuntum mooqineen
  26,25,Qaala liman hawlahooo alaa tastami'oon
  26,26,Qaala Rabbukum wa Rabbu aabaaa'ikumul awwaleen
  26,27,Qaala inna Rasoolakumul lazee ursila ilaikum lamajnoon
  26,28,Qaala Rabbul mashriqi wal maghribi wa maa baina humaa in kuntum ta'qiloon
  26,29,Qaala la'init takhazta ilaahan ghairee la aj'alannaka minal masjooneen
  26,30,Qaala awalw ji'tuka bishai'im mubeen
  26,31,Qaala faati biheee in kunta minas saadiqeen
  26,32,Fa alqaa 'asaahu fa izaaa hiya su'baanum mubeen
  26,33,Wa naza'a yadahoo faizaa hiya baidaaa'u linnaa zireen (section 2)
  26,34,Qaala lilmala-i hawlahooo inna haazaa lasaahirun 'aleem
  26,35,Yureedu ai yukhrijakum min ardikum bisihrihee famaazaa taamuroon
  26,36,Qaalooo arjih wa akhaahu wab'as filmadaaa'ini haashireen
  26,37,Yaatooka bikulli sah haarin 'aleem
  26,38,Fa jumi'as saharatu limeeqaati Yawmim ma'loom
  26,39,Wa qeela linnaasi hal antum mujtami'oon
  26,40,La'allanaa nattabi'us saharata in kaanoo humul ghaalibeen
  26,41,Falammaa jaaa'as saharatu qaaloo li Fir'awna a'inna lanaa la ajjran in kunnaa nahnul ghaalibeen
  26,42,Qaala na'am wa innakum izal laminal muqarrabeen
  26,43,Qaala lahum Moosaaa alqoo maaa antum mulqoon
  26,44,Fa alqaw hibaalahum wa 'isiyyahum wa qaaloo bi'izzati Fir'awna innaa lanahnul ghaaliboon
  26,45,Fa alqaa Moosaa 'asaahu fa izaa hiya talqafu maa yaafikoon
  26,46,Fa ulqiyas saharatu saajideen
  26,47,Qaalooo aamannaa bi Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,48,Rabbi Moosaa wa Haaroon
  26,49,Qaala aamantum lahoo qabla an aazana lakum innahoo lakabeerukumul lazee 'alla makumus sihra falasawfa ta'lamoon; la uqatti'anna aidiyakum wa arjulakum min khilaafinw wa la usallibanna kum ajma'een
  26,50,Qaaloo la daira innaaa ilaa Rabbinaa munqalliboon
  26,51,Innaa natma'u ai yaghfira lanaa Rabbunna khataa yaanaaa an kunnaaa awwalal mu'mineen (section 3)
  26,52,Wa awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa an asri bi'ibaadeee innakum muttaba'oon
  26,53,Fa arsala Fir'awnu filmadaaa'ini haashireen
  26,54,Inna haaa'ulaaa'i lashir zimatun qaleeloon
  26,55,Wa innahum lanaa laghaaa'izoon
  26,56,Wa innaa lajamee'un haaziroon
  26,57,Fa akhrajnaahum min Jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
  26,58,Wa kunoozinw wa ma qaamin kareem
  26,59,Kazaalika wa awrasnaahaa Baneee Israaa'eel
  26,60,Fa atba'oohum mushriqeen
  26,61,Falammaa taraaa'al jam'aani qaala as haabu Moosaaa innaa lamudrakoon
  26,62,Qaala kallaaa inna ma'iya Rabbee sa yahdeen
  26,63,Fa awhainaaa ilaa Moosaaa anidrib bi'asaakal bahra fanfalaqa fakaana kullu firqin kattawdil 'azeem
  26,64,Wa azlafnaa sammal aakhareen
  26,65,Wa anjainaa Moosaa wa mam ma'ahooo ajma'een
  26,66,Summa aghraqnal aakhareen
  26,67,Inna fee zaalika la Aayaah; wa maa kaana aksaru hu mu'mineen
  26,68,Wa inna Rabbaka la Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 4)
  26,69,Watlu 'alaihim naba-a Ibraaheem
  26,70,Iz qaala li abeehi wa qawmihee maa ta'budoon
  26,71,Qaaloo na'budu asnaaman fanazallu lahaa 'aakifeen
  26,72,Qaala hal yasma'oona kum iz tad'oon
  26,73,Aw yanfa'oonakum aw yadurroon
  26,74,Qaaloo bal wajadnaaa aabaaa 'anaa kazaalika yaf'aloon
  26,75,Qaala afara 'aitum maa kuntum ta'budoon
  26,76,Antum wa aabaaa'ukumul aqdamoon
  26,77,Fa innahum 'aduwwwul leee illaa Rabbal 'aalameen
  26,78,Allazee khalaqanee fa Huwa yahdeen
  26,79,Wallazee Huwa yut'imunee wa yasqeen
  26,80,Wa izaa mardtu fahuwa yashfeen
  26,81,Wallazee yumeetunee summa yuhyeen
  26,82,Wallazeee atma'u ai yaghfira lee khateee' atee Yawmad Deen
  26,83,Rabbi hab lee hukmanw wa alhiqnee bis saaliheen
  26,84,Waj'al lee lisaana sidqin fil aakhireen
  26,85,Waj'alnee minw warasati Jannnatin Na'eem
  26,86,Waghfir li abeee innahoo kaana mind daalleen
  26,87,Wa laa tukhzinee Yawma yub'asoon
  26,88,Yawma laa yanfa'u maalunw wa laa banoon
  26,89,Illaa man atal laaha biqalbin saleem
  26,90,Wa uzlifatil Jannatu lilmuttaqeen
  26,91,Wa burrizatil Jaheemu lilghaaween
  26,92,Wa qeela lahum aina maa kuntum ta'budoon
  26,93,Min doonil laahi hal yansuroonakum aw yantasiroon
  26,94,Fakubkiboo feehaa hum walghaawoon
  26,95,Wa junoodu Ibleesa ajma'oon
  26,96,Qaaloo wa hum feehaa yakkhtasimoon
  26,97,Tallaahi in kunnaa lafee dalaalim mubeen
  26,98,Iz nusawweekum bi Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,99,Wa maaa adallanaaa illal mujrimoon
  26,100,Famaa lanaa min shaa fi'een
  26,101,Wa laa sadeeqin hameem
  26,102,Falaw anna lanaa karratan fanakoona minal mu'mineen
  26,103,Inna fee zaalika la Aayatanw wa maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen
  26,104,Wa inna Rabbaka la Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 5)
  26,105,Kazzabat qawmu Noohinil Mursaleen
  26,106,Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Noohun alaa tattaqoon
  26,107,Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen
  26,108,Fattaqullaaha wa atee'oon
  26,109,Wa maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,110,Fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  26,111,Qaalooo anu'minu laka wattaba 'akal arzaloon
  26,112,Qaala wa maa 'ilmee bimaa kaanoo ya'maloon
  26,113,In hisaabuhum illaa 'alaa Rabbee law tash'uroon
  26,114,Wa maaa ana bitaaridil mu'mineen
  26,115,In ana illaa nazeerum mubeen
  26,116,Qaaloo la'il lam tantahi yaa Noohu latakoonanna minal marjoomeen
  26,117,Qaala Rabbi inna qawmee kazzaboon
  26,118,Faftab bainee wa bai nahum fat hanw wa najjinee wa mam ma'iya minal mu'mineen
  26,119,Fa anjainaahu wa mamma'ahoo fil fulkil mashhoon
  26,120,Summa aghraqnaa ba'dul baaqeen
  26,121,Inna fee zaalika la Aayaah; wa maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen
  26,122,Wa inna Rabbaka la huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 6)
  26,123,Kazzabat 'Aadunil mursaleen
  26,124,Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Hoodun alaa tattaqoon
  26,125,Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen
  26,126,Fattaqullaaha wa atee'oon
  26,127,Wa maa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,128,Atabnoona bikulli ree'in aayatan ta'basoon
  26,129,Wa tattakhizoona masaani'a la'allakum takhludoon
  26,130,Wa izaa batashtum batashtum jabbaareen
  26,131,Fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  26,132,Wattaqul lazeee amad dakum bimaa ta'lamoon
  26,133,Amaddakum bi an'aa minw wa baneen
  26,134,Wa jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
  26,135,Innee akhaafu 'alaikum 'azaaba Yawmin 'azeem
  26,136,Qaaloo sawaaa'un 'alainaaa awa 'azta am lam takum minal waa'izeen
  26,137,In haazaaa illaa khuluqul awwaleen
  26,138,Wa maa nahnu bimu 'azzabeen
  26,139,Fakazzaboohu fa ahlaknaahum; inna fee zaalika la aayah; wa maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen
  26,140,Wa inna Rabbaka la huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 7)
  26,141,Kazzabat Samoodul mursaleen
  26,142,Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Saalihun alaa tattaqoon
  26,143,Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen
  26,144,Fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  26,145,Wa maaa as'alukum 'alaihi� min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,146,Atutrakoona fee maa haahunnaaa aamineen
  26,147,Fee jannaatinw wa 'uyoon
  26,148,Wa zuroo inw wa nakhlin tal 'uhaa hadeem
  26,149,Wa tanhitoona minal jibaali buyootan faariheen
  26,150,Fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  26,151,Wa laa tutee'ooo amral musrifeen
  26,152,Allazeena yufsidoona fil ardi wa laa yuslihoon
  26,153,Qaalooo innamaa anta minal musahhareen
  26,154,Maaa anta illaa basharum mislunaa faati bi Aayatin in kunta minas saadiqeen
  26,155,Qaala haazihee naaqatul lahaa shirbunw w alakum shirbu yawmim ma'loom
  26,156,Wa laa tamassoohaa bisooo'in fa yaakhuzakum 'azaabu Yawmin 'Azeem
  26,157,Fa'aqaroohaa fa asbahoo naadimeen
  26,158,Fa akhazahumul 'azaab; inna fee zaalika la Aayah; wa maa kaana aksaruhum m'mineen
  26,159,Wa inna Rabbaka la Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 8)
  26,160,kazzabat qawmu Lootinil mursaleen
  26,161,Iz qaala lahum akhoohum Lootun alaa tattaqoon
  26,162,Innee lakum rasoolun ameen
  26,163,Fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  26,164,Wa maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,165,Ataatoonaz zukraana minal 'aalameen
  26,166,Wa tazaroona maa khalaqa lakum Rabbukum min azwaajikum; bal antum qawmun 'aadoon
  26,167,Qaloo la'il lam tantahi yaa Lootu latakoonanna minal mukhrajeen
  26,168,Qaala innee li'amalikum minal qaaleen
  26,169,Rabbi najjjinee wa ahlee mimmmaa ya'maloon
  26,170,Fanajjainaahu wa ahlahooo ajma'een
  26,171,Illaa 'ajoozan filghaabireen
  26,172,Summa dammarnal aa khareen
  26,173,Wa amtarnaa 'alaihim mataran fasaaa'a matarul munzareen
  26,174,Inna fee zaalika la Aayah; wa maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen
  26,175,Wa inna Rabbaka la Huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (section 9)
  26,176,Kazzaba As haabul Aykatil mursaleen
  26,177,Iz qaala lahum Shu'aybun alaa tattaqoon
  26,178,Innee lakum Rasoolun ameen
  26,179,Fattaqul laaha wa atee'oon
  26,180,Wa maaa as'alukum 'alaihi min ajrin in ajriya illaa 'alaa Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,181,Awful kaila wa laa takoonoo minal mukhsireen
  26,182,Wa zinoo bilqistaasil mustaqeem
  26,183,Wa laa tabkhasun naasa ashyaaa 'ahum wa laa ta'saw fil ardi mufsideen
  26,184,Wattaqul lazee khalaqakum waljibillatal awwaleen
  26,185,Qaalooo innamaa anta minal musahhareen
  26,186,Wa maaa anta illaa basharum mislunaa wa innazunnuka laminal kaazibeen
  26,187,Fa asqit 'alainaa kisafam minas samaaa'i in kunta minas saadiqeen
  26,188,Qaala Rabbeee a'lamu bimaa ta'maloon
  26,189,Fakazzaboohu fa akhazahum 'azaabu Yawmiz zullah; innahoo kaana 'azaaba Yawmin 'Azeem
  26,190,Inna fee zaalika la Aayah; wa maa kaana aksaruhum mu'mineen
  26,191,Wa inna Rabbaka la huwal 'Azeezur Raheem (secion 10)
  26,192,Wa innahoo latanzeelu Rabbil 'aalameen
  26,193,Nazala bihir Roohul Ameen
  26,194,'Alaa qalbika litakoona minal munzireen
  26,195,Bilisaanin 'Arabiyyim mubeen
  26,196,Wa innahoo lafee Zuburil awwaleen
  26,197,Awalam yakul lahum Aayatan ai ya'lamahoo 'ulamaaa'u Baneee Israaa'eel
  26,198,Wa law nazzalnaahu 'alaa ba'dil a'jameen
  26,199,Faqara ahoo 'alaihim maa kaanoo bihee mu'mineen
  26,200,Kazaalika salaknaahu fee quloobil mujrimeen
  26,201,Laa yu'minoona bihee hattaa yarawul 'azaabal aleem
  26,202,Fayaatiyahum baghtatanw wa hum laa yash'uroon
  26,203,Fa yaqooloo hal nahnu munzaroon
  26,204,Aafabi 'azaabinaa yasta'jiloon
  26,205,Aara'aita im matta'naahum sineen
  26,206,Summa jaaa'ahum maa kaanoo yoo'adoon
  26,207,Maaa aghnaaa 'anhum maa kaanoo yumaatoo'oon
  26,208,Wa maaa ahlaknaa min qaryatin illaa lahaa munziroon
  26,209,Zikraa wa maa kunnaa zaalimeen
  26,210,Wa maa tanazzalat bihish Shayaateen
  26,211,Wa maa yambaghee lahum wa maa yastatee'oon
  26,212,Innahum 'anis sam'i lama'zooloon
  26,213,Falaa tad'u ma'al laahi ilaahan aakhara fatakoona minal mu'azzabeen
  26,214,Wa anzir 'asheeratakal aqrabeen
  26,215,Wakhfid janaahaka limanit taba 'aka minal mu'mineen
  26,216,Fa in asawka faqul innee bareee'um mimmmaa ta'maloon
  26,217,Wa tawakkal alal 'Azeezir Raheem
  26,218,Allazee yaraaka heena taqoom
  26,219,Wa taqallubaka fis saajideen
  26,220,Innahoo Huwas Samee'ul 'Aleem
  26,221,Hal unabbi'ukum 'alaa man tanazzalush Shayaateen
  26,222,Tanazzalu 'alaa kulli affaakin aseem
  26,223,Yulqoonas sam'a wa aksaruhum aaziboon
  26,224,Washshu 'araaa'u yattabi 'uhumul ghaawoon
  26,225,Alam tara annahum fee kulli waadiny yaheemoon
  26,226,Wa annahum yaqooloona ma laa yaf'aloon
  26,227,Illal lazeena aamanoo w a'amilus saalihaati wa zakarul laaha kaseeranw wantasaroo mim ba'di maa zulimoo; wa saya'lamul lazeena zalamooo aiya munqalbiny yanqaliboon (section 11)
